<h1>Unified Parkinson's Advocacy Council</h1>
<p>The Michael J. Fox Foundation works with other Parkinson’s disease groups to advance policies that benefit patients, families and caregivers through the Unified Parkinson’s Advocacy Council (UPAC).</p>
<p>The UPAC comprises representatives from state, regional and national PD organizations to gather field-wide input on priorities and policy matters.</p>
<p>UPAC members include:</p>
